This paper deals with the problem of predicting the subjective quality of HTTP-based video streaming, which involves machine learning techniques and network analysis. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-categories.
